  "text": "The soluble protein powder (ORIHIRO, Tokyo, Japan) was used to prepare the 10 synthetic wastewater as the substrate. The powder is derived from soy protein. [CITATION_1] protein powder are made by protein (81.2 %), lipid (1-5 %), carbohydrate (2-12 %). 12",
